{"pageProps":{"body":"<h1 id=\"oshw-project-management-user-stories\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#oshw-project-management-user-stories\"></a>OSHW Project Management User Stories</h1>\n<h2 id=\"preamble\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#preamble\"></a>Preamble</h2>\n<p>Welcome to the <em>How do you share your Open-Source Hardware project</em> workshop summary report. During the workshop we worked with participants to identify what we can do as a community to make it easier to share, communicate, and collaborate on OSHW projects. The following content is the result of that work.</p>\n<h2 id=\"0-workshop\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#0-workshop\"></a><a href=\"/template.publish.github-action/notes/xox7exjnhcxnab73bxyrblt\">0. Workshop</a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"/template.publish.github-action/assets/oshw-logo.svg\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p></p><p></p><div class=\"portal-container\">\n<div class=\"portal-head\">\n<div class=\"portal-backlink\">\n<div class=\"portal-title\">From <span class=\"portal-text-title\">0. Workshop</span></div>\n<a href=\"/template.publish.github-action/notes/xox7exjnhcxnab73bxyrblt\" class=\"portal-arrow\">Go to text <span class=\"right-arrow\">→</span></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"portal-parent-anchor\" class=\"portal-parent\" markdown=\"1\">\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-top\"></div>\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-bottom\"></div><h2 id=\"1-audience-survey\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-audience-survey\"></a><a href=\"/template.publish.github-action/notes/py9pnyni5n8iwwbgqmfsad1\">1. Audience Survey</a></h2>\n<p></p><p></p><div class=\"portal-container\">\n<div class=\"portal-head\">\n<div class=\"portal-backlink\">\n<div class=\"portal-title\">From <span class=\"portal-text-title\">1. Audience Survey</span></div>\n<a href=\"/template.publish.github-action/notes/py9pnyni5n8iwwbgqmfsad1\" clas